Well, to sum up my day [so far.] I woke up, me and Sammy went to Lemoore so he could get a hair cut. ;P Came home, had a lil' drama, but it was soon fixed, finished getting ready and we went to Visalia, Sammy and I went to the mall and he bought me these cute earrings and he played DDR. -_- Haha, then he took me to dinner at this chinese resturant in Visalia, and it was goooood and we saved our little fortunes from our fortune cookies (= In [memorie] of our first Valentines Day together. ^_^ Then there was more DDR. -_- and we saw the guitarist from Brand New! Hahah ;P Then he took me to starbucks and got me my Taffe Nut Latte` (= Ohh yeah and my coffee cake. ^_^ Then we went to my uncles to visit my lil' cousins we haven't seen in years and me and Sammy layed on the couch with the little puppy [Jack.] and then yeah he played with Alyssa and Seth. Then we came home ohhh and Sammy got me roses today for Valentines day and they are soo hella pretty. ^_^ And he even got my mom one too. (= Yeah so now we're home and like we're gonna go watch a movie and stuff and imma prolly fall asleep. ;P But yeah all I need is to be in his arms and i'll be happy. Coz' yanno it's only 10:10, there is still 1 hour and 50 minutes left of Valentines Day. ^_^ Okay well that's my day [in a nut shell.] Haha, more later, if I feel like it. Oh yeah Sammy got me and him these hella cute bracelets, haha And my mom. -_- Haha okay bye!

Well well well, long time no post. I have nothing to quite say. Umm let's see a lot has gone on. I think the best part out of my whole weekend was this..

So im trying to fix my computer so my mom doesn't get all pissed and say "why did I even get you cable internet for if your comp. doesn't work? that things brand new! blah blah blah"  So I re-format it, and go to instal Windows XP again.. and it WON'T WORK.. and I start crying coz' omg im stupid and I fucked up my computer.. so Sammys like sitting at my comp. desk and im like right by him on my bed crying and shit and he's all "come here princess" and he puts me on his lap and my heads like burried into his neck crying still and he like kisses my head and starts rocking me and hes all "shh its okay princess i'll fix it for you" and then like I stop crying and I look at him and he's like " I love you Princess *smiles* " and he kisses my cheek. So then I go to get my cheez-its, haha and whadda ya know! Sammy fixes my computer for me!! Muahh hahaha! Yay! (= So yeah I thought that was a pretty moment and it made me smile, coz' it was really sweet of him. *sigh* Well.. I know those of you that know of whats been goin' on between me and sammy are wonderin' right now, well you can keep it up! Haha.. Yeah well anyways, Valentines Day is on Saturday. Can't wait! (=

Ohhh and before I forget, Sammy and Brother Jay, I looked up the lyrics to Sic Transit Gloria for you guys, just to PROVE that once again I' am right! Hahah ^_^:

She hits the lights.
This doesn't seem quite fair.
Despite everything he learned from his friends,
he doesn't feel so prepared.
She's breathing quiet and smooth.
He's gasping for air.
"This is the first and last time," he says.
She fakes a smile and presses her hips into his.
He keeps his hands pinned down at his sides.
He's holding back from telling her
exactly what it really feels...

like.

He is the lamb, she is the slaughter.
She's moving way too fast and all he wanted was to hold her.
Nothing that he tells her is really having an effect.
He whispers that he loves her,
but she's probably only looking for...

Some fucking pissed off times with Vanessa. Some fucked up family times. And what not. Today should be fun though, I'm goin' shoppin' with Jay, around 2 or so.. imma go buy Sammy a couple things.. then imma buy me a damn new purse! Don't know What I was looking for when I went home

beneath the dark atlantic sky..
